
All the APIs can only be accesses from POST method


APIs are listed below as per the user stories

1. As a user, I need an API to create a friend connection between two email addresses.
(http://localhost:8080/spgroup/connect_friends)

2. As a user, I need an API to retrieve the friends list for an email address.
http://localhost:8080/spgroup/fetch_friends

3. As a user, I need an API to retrieve the common friends list between two email addresses.
http://localhost:8080/spgroup/fetch_common_friends

4. As a user, I need an API to subscribe to updates from an email address.
http://localhost:8080/spgroup/subscribe_email

5. As a user, I need an API to block updates from an email address.
http://localhost:8080/spgroup/block_email

6. As a user, I need an API to retrieve all email addresses that can receive updates from an email address.
http://localhost:8080/spgroup/fetch_update_emails



The application can be run using below command as well.
 java -jar target/friend_management-0.0.1-SNAPSHOT.jar
